         <note href="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.xml#Reference_Library-69E2C789/ForRedundantSystemsCheckThatEachSte-0FD805BD"
               otherprops="typeR">For redundant systems:  Check that each
step is perform on both units before proceeding to next step.</note>
         <note href="../Library/Reference_Library_CPT_0000338844.xml#Reference_Library-69E2C789/ForDualSystemsPerformAllTheStepsOnO-0FD807C7"
               otherprops="typeD">For dual systems: Perform all the steps
on one unit, then repeat the complete procedure for the other unit.</note>
         <p>
            <ol>
               <li>
                  <p>Check that the system is in <ph platform="PxW WxW">normal operation</ph>
                     <ph platform="SDC">float charge</ph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li platform="PxW WxW">
                  <p>For systems with a bypass: Open the
bypass mains breaker to disconnect the bypass.</p>
               </li>
               <li>
                  <p>Press both the ON button and the OFF button at
the same time for two seconds. The Display shows <codeph>Standby</codeph>.</p>
               </li>
               <li platform="PxW SDC">
                  <p>Open the battery breaker to disconnect the
battery bank.</p>
               </li>
               <li platform="PxW SDC">
                  <p>Open the rectifier mains breaker to turn
off the power supply to the rectifier.</p>
               </li>
               <li platform="WxW">
                  <p>Switch off the source of the DC power supply.</p>
               </li>
               <li platform="WxW">
                  <p>Open the inverter input switch to disconnect
the DC power supply.</p>
               </li>
               <li platform="WxW">
                  <p>Discharge the DC capacitor by keeping the charging/discharge
switch in position 1 until the warning LED turns off.</p>
               </li>
            </ol>After about 30 seconds the Display and all LEDs are off.
The system is turned off and the load is not supplied anymore.</p>
